{
  "stem": "21013.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I would cut little windows out, like little Austrian cottages with flowerboxes and things like that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that's how I supported myself, make pocket money.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I was teaching German to a few people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I don't-- I mean, they were so kind.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "This was during the war, mind you, with Germany the enemy, and they they did that for me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So they were just wonderful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I really renewed my faith in humanity after that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it affected me because the planes were overhead.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we lived right near Gatwick Airport, which is now a-- a commercial airport.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At that time, it was an army airport.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were no bombings when I was there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The major bombings and V- V-2 rockets came after I left.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My parents experienced all of that, but I didn't.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was afraid, because from early childhood on, I always learned about gas wars and about poison gas and stuff like that, so I was deathly afraid of the war.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- but I didn't want to leave England.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I wanted to stay there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But when my visa came through in November 1939, my parents insisted that I go to America, that I don't stay there, although I really didn't want to leave.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that's when I left.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "What I didn't tell you before was in Vienna, when Hitler marched in, the Nazis took over my grandparents' farm.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "My grandmother was forced to leave the little town where they lived in her beautiful house, and moved in with my aunt and uncle in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My grandmother, Theresa Kohn, and my aunt Camilla Kohn-- Grunwald.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And both of them subsequently died in concentration camp in Poland, in Lublin.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I don't know what year.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I wrote to them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Saying goodbye to my grandmother was also very hard.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
